TemplateDef.Name: GetIncurredByFinancialGroup
TemplateDef.ExpressionPrototype: If(($financialGroup$ < 1) or ($financialGroup$ > 4), 0, If($financialGroup$ = 1, If(Claim.Status <> "C", Largest(Claim.Reserved_Group1, Claim.Paid_Group1), Claim.Paid_Group1), If($financialGroup$ = 2, If(Claim.Status <> "C", Largest(Claim.Reserved_Group2, Claim.Paid_Group2), Claim.Paid_Group2), If($financialGroup$ = 3, If(Claim.Status <> "C", Largest(Claim.Reserved_Group3, Claim.Paid_Group3), Claim.Paid_Group3), If($financialGroup$ = 4, If(Claim.Status <> "C", Largest(Claim.Reserved_Group4, Claim.Paid_Group4), Claim.Paid_Group4), 0)))))
